"system and handled by <systemitem class=\"daemon\">systemd</systemitem>. "
"<systemitem class=\"daemon\">systemd</systemitem> provides a set of "
"<quote>targets</quote> that boot configurations for everyday usage, "
"maintenance or emergencies."
